name: Bodyweight Squat
description: Fundamental lower body exercise. Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, lower hips back and down, keep chest up.

name: Push-up
description: Classic upper body exercise. Start in plank position, lower chest to ground, push back up.

name: Plank Hold
description: Core stability exercise. Hold straight body position on forearms and toes.

name: Walking Lunges
description: Dynamic lower body exercise. Step forward, lower back knee, alternate legs.

name: Pike Push-up
description: Shoulder-focused push-up variation. Start in downward dog position, lower head toward ground.

name: Burpees
description: High-intensity full body exercise. Squat, jump back to plank, push-up, jump forward, jump up.

name: Mountain Climbers
description: Dynamic core and cardio exercise. Plank position, alternate bringing knees to chest rapidly.

name: Jump Squats
description: Plyometric lower body exercise. Perform squat, explode upward into a jump.

name: Tricep Dips (Chair)
description: Upper body pushing exercise. Use chair or bench, lower body by bending elbows, push back up.

name: Glute Bridge
description: Hip extension exercise. Lie on back, lift hips up, squeeze glutes at top.

name: Single-Leg Glute Bridge
description: Advanced glute bridge. Perform with one leg extended.

name: High Knees
description: Cardio exercise. Run in place bringing knees high.

name: Jumping Jacks
description: Classic cardio exercise. Jump legs apart while raising arms overhead.

name: Side Plank (Each Side)
description: Lateral core stability. Hold body straight on one forearm and side of feet.

name: Bicycle Crunches
description: Rotational core exercise. Alternate bringing opposite elbow to knee.

name: Dead Bug
description: Core stability exercise. Lie on back, alternate extending opposite arm and leg.

name: Bird Dog
description: Back and core stability. On hands and knees, extend opposite arm and leg.

name: Inchworm Walk-out
description: Dynamic warm-up and core exercise. Walk hands out to plank, walk back to feet.

name: Squat Jumps
description: Explosive lower body exercise. Squat then jump maximally.

name: Diamond Push-ups
description: Tricep-focused push-up. Hands form diamond shape under chest.

name: Wide-Grip Push-ups
description: Chest-focused push-up. Hands placed wider than shoulder-width.

name: Decline Push-ups
description: Push-up with feet elevated. Increases difficulty and targets upper chest.

name: Bulgarian Split Squat (Bodyweight)
description: Single-leg squat with rear foot elevated on chair/bench.

name: Cossack Squats
description: Lateral squat shifting weight side to side. Improves mobility.

name: Wall Sit
description: Static hold against wall in squat position.

name: Superman Hold
description: Lie face down, lift arms and legs off ground simultaneously.

name: Hollow Body Hold
description: Lie on back, lift shoulders and legs off ground, hold.

name: Flutter Kicks
description: Lie on back, small rapid kicks with straight legs.

name: Russian Twists (Bodyweight)
description: Seated, lean back slightly, rotate torso side to side.

name: Bear Crawl
description: Crawl on hands and feet (knees off ground) forward and backward.

name: Crab Walk
description: Walk backwards on hands and feet (belly up).

name: Skater Hops
description: Lateral bound from one leg to another.

name: Broad Jumps
description: Jump forward maximally from standing position.

name: Tuck Jumps
description: Jump bringing knees to chest.

name: Dumbbell Goblet Squat
description: Hold one dumbbell at chest, perform squat.

name: Dumbbell Romanian Deadlift

name: Dumbbell Bench Press

name: Dumbbell Row (Single-Arm)

name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
description: Press dumbbells overhead from shoulder height.

name: Dumbbell Bicep Curl
description: Curl dumbbells from sides up to shoulders.

name: Dumbbell Hammer Curl
description: Curl dumbbells with neutral grip (palms facing each other).

name: Dumbbell Overhead Tricep Extension

name: Dumbbell Lateral Raise
description: Raise dumbbells out to sides to shoulder height.

name: Dumbbell Front Raise
description: Raise dumbbells forward to shoulder height.

name: Dumbbell Chest Fly
description: Lie on bench, arc dumbbells out to sides and back up.

name: Dumbbell Pullover
description: Lie across bench, lower dumbbell behind head in arc.

name: Dumbbell Lunges
description: Perform lunges holding dumbbells at sides.

name: Dumbbell Step-ups
description: Step up onto box/bench holding dumbbells.

name: Dumbbell Shrugs

name: Dumbbell Skull Crushers

name: Dumbbell Farmers Walk

name: Barbell Back Squat

name: Barbell Bench Press

name: Barbell Romanian Deadlift

name: Barbell Hip Thrust

name: Barbell Front Squat

name: Barbell Curl

name: Barbell Skull Crusher

name: Pull-up
